snippet.title: Fortune Cookie Java Program - Build a Fortune Program in 11 Minutes
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- HUGE ANNOUNCEMENT!!!! I have my own merch now :) I had no idea what I was doing in school, or even now so I wanted to make apparel to embrace this feeling. Let the world know you are clueless with my new "I have no idea what I'm doing" shirts and hoodies! https://teespring.com/i-have-no-idea-what-do-2020

Here's a quick, 4 line program that will help you practice the basics in java. I hope this fortune cookie program in java helps you practice a little!

This is a simple java program to help you practice java programming :) -
